videos.description: No. 14 Illinois pulls away from UT Rio Grande Valley late as Kofi Cockburn scores two of his 38 points with a two-handed slam in the final minutes.
videos.headline: Kofi Cockburn flushes clutch dunk as Illinois survives upset scare
